<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#fff4ee">
    <title>Đăng nhập</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --brand-primary: #ee4d2d;
            --brand-secondary: #ff835f;
            --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            --surface-border: rgba(255, 130, 90, 0.18);
            --text-primary: #1f2937;
            --text-secondary: #6b7280;
            --success: #0f8a4b;
            --success-bg: #edfdf3;
            --danger: #b42318;
            --danger-bg: #fff1f0;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.2), transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at right center, rgba(255, 157, 112, 0.16), transparent 26%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8f5 0%, #fff1ea 48%, #ffe5dc 100%);
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .login-shell {
            width: min(1080px, 100%);
            min-height: min(740px, calc(100vh - 48px));
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.12fr) minmax(360px, 440px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.44);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
            border-radius: 28px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(184, 68, 30, 0.18);
        }

        .login-hero {
            position: relative;
            padding: 48px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background:
                linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.96) 0%, rgba(255, 133, 84, 0.92) 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .login-hero::before,
        .login-hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .login-hero::before {
            width: 360px;
            height: 360px;
            top: -120px;
            right: -110px;
        }

        .login-hero::after {
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            bottom: -70px;
            left: -60px;
        }

        .hero-brand,
        .hero-content,
        .hero-footnote {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 4rem);
            line-height: 1.02;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            text-wrap: balance;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            max-width: 30rem;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
        }

        .hero-points {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .hero-point {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .hero-point i {
            width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-footnote {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        .login-panel {
            background: var(--surface);
            padding: 44px 36px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .panel-intro {
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.08);
            color: var(--brand-primary);
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h2 {
            margin: 16px 0 8px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            text-wrap: balance;
        }

        .panel-intro p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        form {
            display: grid;
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .form-group {
            display: grid;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-size: 0.94rem;
        }

        .input-with-icon {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-with-icon i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 14px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #9ca3af;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 52px;
            padding: 14px 16px 14px 44px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.18);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
            font-size: 0.96rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
            border-color: rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.58);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.12);
            outline: none;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus + i,
        input[type="password"]:focus + i {
            color: var(--brand-primary);
        }

        input::placeholder {
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        input:focus-visible,
        button:focus-visible,
        a:focus-visible {
            outline: 3px solid rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.18);
            outline-offset: 2px;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 52px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-primary) 0%, var(--brand-secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, filter 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(238, 77, 45, 0.24);
            touch-action: manipulation;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            filter: brightness(0.98);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .status-message {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 0.94rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .status-message i {
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .status-message.error {
            color: var(--danger);
            background: var(--danger-bg);
            border-color: rgba(180, 35, 24, 0.12);
        }

        .status-message.success {
            color: var(--success);
            background: var(--success-bg);
            border-color: rgba(15, 138, 75, 0.12);
        }

        .register-link {
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.94rem;
        }

        .register-link a {
            color: var(--brand-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .register-link a:hover {
            color: #c73717;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .helper-copy {
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .login-shell {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                min-height: auto;
            }

            .login-hero {
                padding: 32px 28px 24px;
                min-height: 280px;
            }

            .login-panel {
                padding: 30px 24px 28px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            body {
                padding: 12px;
            }

            .login-shell {
                border-radius: 22px;
            }

            .login-hero {
                padding: 28px 22px 22px;
            }

            .login-panel {
                padding: 26px 20px 24px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            *, *::before, *::after {
                animation: none !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                scroll-behavior: auto !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-shell">
        <section class="login-hero" aria-label="Giới thiệu hệ thống">
      

            <div class="hero-content">
                <h2>Upload Video Manager</h2>
                <p>Nền tảng hỗ trợ Affiliate và Customer.</p>

               
            </div>

            <div class="hero-footnote">
                <i class="fas fa-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <span>Phiên làm việc được bảo vệ và truy cập bằng tài khoản nội bộ.</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="login-panel" aria-labelledby="login-title">
            <div class="panel-intro">
                <span class="eyebrow">Đăng nhập hệ thống</span>
                <h2 id="login-title">Chào mừng quay lại</h2>
                <p>Nhập tài khoản để tiếp tục vào khu quản trị và công cụ vận hành.</p>
            </div>

            <% if (locals.error) { %>
                <div class="status-message error" aria-live="polite">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <span><%= error %></span>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (locals.success) { %>
                <div class="status-message success" aria-live="polite">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <span><%= success %></span>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="username">Tên đăng nhập</label>
                    <div class="input-with-icon">
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            id="username"
                            name="username"
                            autocomplete="username"
                            spellcheck="false"
                            required
                            placeholder="Nhập tên đăng nhập…">
                        <i class="fas fa-user" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Mật khẩu</label>
                    <div class="input-with-icon">
                        <input
                            type="password"
                            id="password"
                            name="password"
                            autocomplete="current-password"
                            required
                            placeholder="Nhập mật khẩu…">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit">
                    <i class="fas fa-right-to-bracket" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Đăng nhập
                </button>
            </form>

            <p class="helper-copy">Nếu có lỗi đăng nhập, kiểm tra lại tên tài khoản hoặc liên hệ quản trị viên.</p>

            <div class="register-link">
                <p>Chưa có tài khoản? <a href="/register">Đăng ký ngay</a></p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
